{"tid":332132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獨居男暴斃逾十日傳惡臭 鄰居：以為有人煮蝦醬","createTime":"2017-07-22T17:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T01:19:32.000Z","uid":22349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de77a142684a321d882b704aa62cca2189d460d9","tid":332132,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T17:51:33.000Z","msg":"屍臭味，竟然似臭蝦醬味？！山東青島市武寧路一處屋苑臭味彌漫了十幾天，樓主報警後才發現一名中年男子在家中死亡。鄰居表示，事發前兩天已聞到一陣臭味，以為是那一戶人家煮蝦醬，說清楚一點應該是似臭蝦醬味道。<br />\n<br />\n樓主表示，到場調查警員曾勸她不要進事發單位，表示看見那具屍體後會發噩夢。警方指，遇事男子搬往處單位不久，平日喜歡喝酒，估計他已死了一段不知時間，因為最近持續高溫，身上甚至招了蟲子。據悉，男子家中有3兄弟，他是最小，一直沒有工作，是靠父母供養的那種「啃老族」。"},{"pid":"2993436af0df78436344902642d1c2b7dde37ab5","tid":332132,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T17:52:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170723&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=56990121 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170723%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D56990121%20&d=3aNSw6jVxEDekNmPJGIa%2BDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=83e6c269\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170723%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D56990121%20&h=dba680f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170723&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=56990121 </a>"},{"pid":"e1ffda01e9ac901b6c363efcd51fd714f944d840","tid":332132,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T17:58:25.000Z","msg":"咁應該係香定臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a94824d4cb665aab5ed42a765381a5ad48163df3","tid":332132,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T22:23:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4a66d61142d5105b52a0eb1cea631343bdd2af4","tid":332132,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T00:58:44.000Z","msg":"頭幾日都算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n認到第七日打後真係真心佩